---

## Backend API Routes

### `GET /api/sightings`
Returns a merged list of:
- Official Elanco tick sightings (`https://dev-task.elancoapps.com/data/tick-sightings`)
- User-submitted SQLite reports

### `POST /api/report`
Stores a new user report in SQLite.

Payload example:

```json
{
  "date": "2025-01-20",
  "city": "London",
  "environment": "Park",
  "host": "Dog",
  "species": "Marsh tick",
  "latinName": "Ixodes apronophorus",
  "severity": "low",
  "notes": "Found near a tree",
  "email": "example@gmail.com"
}
````

